'''第14屆休士頓影評人協會獎'''（The 14th Houston Film Critics Society Awards）是[[休斯頓影評人協會|休士頓影評人協會]]以茲獎勵[[2020年電影|2020年電影]]的獎項，於2021年1月12日公布入圍名單<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2020-houston-film-critics-society-hfcs-winners|title=The 2020 Houston Film Critics Society (HFCS) Winners|website=下個最佳影片（Next Best Picture）|author=Matt Neglia|date=2021-01-18|accessdate=2021-01-19|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119041624/https://www.nextbestpicture.com/latest/the-2020-houston-film-critics-society-hfcs-winners|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1月18日宣布得獎者<ref>{{cite web|url=https://houstonfilmcritics.com/houston-film-critics-society-presents-its-14th-award-winners/|title=Houston Film Critics Society Presents Its 14th Award Winners|website=[[休斯頓影評人協會|休士頓影評人協會]]|date=2021-01-19|accessdate=2021-02-26|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124195627/https://houstonfilmcritics.com/houston-film-critics-society-presents-its-14th-award-winners/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2月1日宣布德州獨立電影獎得獎名單<ref>{{cite web|url=https://houstonfilmcritics.com/houston-film-critics-society-reveals-tifa-winners/|title=Houston Film Critics Society Reveals TIFA Winners|website=休士頓影評人協會|date=2021-02-01|accessdate=2021-03-15|archive-date=2021-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316090045/https://houstonfilmcritics.com/houston-film-critics-society-reveals-tifa-winners/}}</ref>。

